item.title: CVE-2023-5762|2023-12-04T21:28:22.256Z -- unknown -- filr
item.description: The Filr WordPress plugin before 1.2.3.6 is vulnerable from an RCE (Remote Code Execution) vulnerability, which allows the operating system to execute commands and fully compromise the server on behalf of a user with Author-level privileges.
